                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                  Full-cycle product development from concept to market-ready solution. Complete engineering lifecycle management.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                  <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
